  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Feels like you're wearing nothin' at all!</p><p>Free. </p><p>While you're \"wearing\" this outfit:</p><ul><li><p>You automatically fail any <strong>Wardrobe &amp; Style</strong> checks;</p></li><li><p><strong>Personal Grooming</strong> checks are made at a -3. You'd better hope you look good <em>everywhere. </em></p></li><li><p><strong>Wilderness Survival</strong> checks are also made at a -4 - turns out it's pretty hot and/or cold out.</p></li><li><p>Additionally, people <em>will</em> stop and stare. If you're hot, they'll stop and stare for longer. </p></li><li><p>It's also distracting, but unfortunately not in a good way - you receive -2 to your <strong>COOL</strong> stat while not wearing clothes.</p></li><li><p>Technically speaking, public indecency is still a crime in Night City, but the NCPD usually doesn't have time to enforce that.</p></li></ul>"
    },
